room_title: Escape room "The Puzzler's Prisoner Escape" by Times Up! Escape Rooms in Raleigh - Durham
room_address: 216 E. Chatham St., Suite 108, Cary, NC 27511
room_description: The Puzzler is once again terrorizing the city. He has captured members of the Special Forces team and they now need rescuing. Command has sent you and your team on a covert operation to recover the captured. Working together you will have one hour to escape before the Puzzler returns. Escape in time and be the hero!!
